# SAP Integration Cost Architect

## Environment Variables
- `GEMINI_API_KEY`: Required for AI-powered architecture optimization recommendations.
- `APP_URL`: Automatically set by the platform.

## Pricing Model (Simulated)
- 1 Message Unit = 250 KB of payload.
- Base cost: $4,000/month (includes first 10,000 messages).
- Tier 1: $0.10 per additional message (10k - 100k).
- Tier 2: $0.05 per additional message (100k+).
